.

node.text:
UA Students vs Pro Heroes! Well, mostly.
Tbh I like how most of them turned out I'm not mad at it 👉👈 If you'd like to know why I made the choices I made -  I wrote a small essay about that on my patreon if you're interested^^
.
If nobody tells anime only the last one is a spoiler no one will know so shh🤐
.
So yeah, next up is, well a fire tutorial for patreon, but after that I wanna draw some more villains ^^ keep in mind that I already did the main 3 though😅 
.
Last thing: it's really weird posting so much without background, but they're designs, so well you know - still weird 👉👈
.
